{"tid":1658963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國瑜：越南對中國的態度 值得台灣人思考和學習","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T15:52:31.000Z","uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7ea115d5e1d6ac95c034c2e6c50573343413cc","tid":1658963,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/4106322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F7307%2F4106322&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=3ba5d54a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/4106322</a><br />\n國民黨總統參選人韓國瑜今正式請假拚大選，昨晚他接受節目專訪時提及越南一句名言「天堂太遠，中國太近」來比喻兩岸關係，他表示，越南如何處理中國的關係，幾年年來都是頭等大事，處理不好就很麻煩，這幾句話很值得台灣人民思考；這也是為什麼他要跟蔡英文總統辯論兩岸政策，因為兩岸問題至關重要，更攸關中華民國的生死存亡，處理得不好整個台灣就會漩入這個大漩渦。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，所謂「天堂太遠，中國太近」，是指對越南人來說天堂很遠，但中國就在眼前，怎麼處理對中國的關係，這是越南人幾千年來的頭等大事，處理得好是不是就進天堂，但處理得不好就很麻煩，這句話值得台灣人民來思考。"},{"pid":"6337a109661567f4cff19840716decda162e0f30","tid":1658963,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"554bd1f18ddf98ddb659ca16af9936fc02a45fc9","tid":1658963,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜：我智障"},{"pid":"4dbcfb6ce5829504d7f8cc04c88e20bc285840d8","tid":1658963,"uid":312333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:55:14.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乃共動畫《長毛雪寶》地圖現爭議性中国南海「九段線」　越南政府下令禁映<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"493d47e45957065f54ff548d5374279ea45203c4","tid":1658963,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dis